<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Edler <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        edell vormals <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> und kauffleute wegen, als den
                                <expan>vorczeite<ex>n</ex></expan> der
                            <expan>hoch<ex>geporn</ex></expan> fürst und
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>
<expan>margr<ex>af</ex></expan> Jost von <expan>Merh<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ir
                        hab und kauffmanschaft <add>zu Prünne</add>
<expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> hat, und als
                            <expan>yecz<ex>unden</ex></expan> Lucz
                            <expan>Steinling<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, czu <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<add><expan>gned<ex>igen</ex></expan></add>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, des künigs czu Beheim gnaden darümb
                                <expan>czekume<ex>n</ex></expan> maint,
                            <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz <add>ir </add>gen
                                <expan>desselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, des künigs
                            <expan>durchleuhtik<ex>eit</ex></expan>,
                            <expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> günstige hilff und
                            <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> gütlich beweisen wöllet, ob den
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dieselb ir habe noch gekert und
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>golten</expan>
<expan>werde<ex>n</ex></expan> möcht. Und tut darynne
                            <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>willig<ex>en</ex></expan> dinste <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> als
                        etc. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
